    "title": "Walk-in Drive Software Engineer at IndiaMart",
    "description": "IndiaMart, one of India's leading organizations, is hiring a Software Engineer for our Aurangabad operations. We offer a competitive salary package along with world-class benefits.\n\nAbout IndiaMart:\nIndiaMart is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Write and execute unit tests and integration tests\n• Write clean, maintainable, and well-documented code\n• Contribute to system architecture and technical design decisions\n• Troubleshoot, debug, and resolve software defects and performance issues\n• Integrate third-party APIs and services\n• Mentor junior developers and conduct knowledge-sharing sessions\n• Implement new features based on product requirements\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Master's degree preferred\n• 1-3 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in CI/CD\n• Proficiency in Agile/Scrum\n• Proficiency in Rust\n• Proficiency in SQL\n• Proficiency in Node.js\n• Proficiency in Java\n• Proficiency in Docker\n• Proficiency in Machine Learning\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Referral bonus program\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Flexible working hours\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Salary Range: 4 LPA - 9 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Aurangabad, Maharashtra, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with IndiaMart!",
